{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995560/extras/battle.gif?t=1740106728\" /><br>Wildkeepers Rising is a roguelite RPG bullet heaven where you\u2019ll tame and train a diverse team of Guardian beasts to destroy the invading monster hordes.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995560/extras/allbuffs-optimize.gif?t=1740106728\" /><br>With some RPG story-elements in between, you\u2019ll face hand-drawn fantasy monsters inspired by the worlds of Akira Toriyama and Jim Henson.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Bullet Heaven </strong> | Shred thousands of monsters in bullet heaven runs<br></li><li><strong>Creature Collector</strong> | Discover, tame, and train magical beasts<br></li><li><strong>Runs &amp; Builds</strong> | Create team synergies with different Guardians<br></li><li><strong>Roguelike Runs</strong> | Take runs with different Wildkeepers wielding different weapons<br></li><li><strong>Progression</strong> | Unlock new Guardians and items and make them stronger between runs<br></li><li><strong>RPG Elements</strong> | Discover a rich world of fantasy heroes and magical monsters.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995560/extras/Grampth_Idle-optimize2.gif?t=1740106728\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Meet the Developers</h2>Lioncode Games is an indie development duo making Wildkeepers in Early Access to support its expansion with community feedback.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2995560?t=1740106728","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995560/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740106728","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995560/910b42e1e77d5752bb82637825f5e3a64bfb49af/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=174010672